{"tid":1417412,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"三毛新風向","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:38:41.000Z","uid":157284,"like":13,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"524bba9dc51956a5d609f4ccfa3c5eeab3b0f47c","tid":1417412,"uid":157284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"今晚好多三毛開嘅假分析真分化。<br />\n有個共通點就係一定講話:不分化，不割蓆。然後加一句「不可以被仇恨蒙蔽雙眼」。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，我哋係靠怒火推動呢場運動；而呢場火嘅燃點者係港共、中共政權。仇恨從來冇蒙蔽我哋雙眼，而係更堅定咗我哋嘅決心。<br />\n<br />\n至於正負評嘅帶動，有巴打分析得好好，我就唔多講。巴絲入去睇，唔好咁易畀人帶風向。<br />\n[置頂] 連登投票系統或已失效<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416815</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be7b9314fdd0a519c5e5a15850702ddb92eb8ccd","tid":1417412,"uid":157284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"唔好畀人帶風向"},{"pid":"f92b1d17365ffa78ded23c60f6851100b03c4b93","tid":1417412,"uid":157284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"a351a4bb718cdba42ecaa0b8902cd524895de4b1","tid":1417412,"uid":157284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:20.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"02fd323ecc28b23924cf35de3934ffcbaced1727","tid":1417412,"uid":157284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:30.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"8e41ad21738ef6c3f11de849eae92fa925e829ab","tid":1417412,"uid":157284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"838992138ecb93b51cc0d83468b834bfc964f130","tid":1417412,"uid":157284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"00c0888fa958485b5d3138b9d4f454efeebc7160","tid":1417412,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/14