hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5154e6ad54c8833f364a82dbdb6fe0413319c145","tid":1417412,"uid":115836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:18:35.000Z","msg":"推動呢場運動係因為公義，因為對民主嘅渴求，而唔係怒火。睇返一次天琦寫比我哋封信，諗返起我哋嘅初衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d7bbe02db9bf9b84fde72f5737e48f101ea9ef","tid":1417412,"uid":132829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:18:00.000Z","msg":"推一下<br />\n問下自己，記唔記得反送中運動嘅初衷係咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418494</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}